Package: veriWrapper
Title: Forecast verification metrics for large datasets
Version: 0.4.0
Date: 2014-11-05
Authors@R: "Jonas Bhend <jonas.bhend@meteoswiss.ch> [aut, cre]"
Description: This package provides functions to simplify application of
    forecast verification metrcis to large datasets. The forecast metrics are
    imported from the SpecsVerification package, a few (mostly deterministic)
    forecast scores are provided with this package. Alternatively, new forecast
    scores can be implemented using the example scores provided in this
    package.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0),
    SpecsVerification
Suggests:
    testthat
License: GPL-3
LazyData: true
